              From 2001 to 2010 Mark sourced and managed venture capital investments for Leo Capital Holdings.
              Recent board of directorship service includes GrubHub, Shoutlet and FunMobility.
              On behalf of Hyde Park Angels, an early stage investor group, he serves as an observer on the
              investment committee of Hyde Park Ventures. He is the founder of WirePoints, an online news site,
