            <p class="lead">
              Ofer is an entrepreneur and a technologist. Most recently, he was CEO of BoldIQ,
              a provider of optimization and management solutions to the aviation, transportation and energy industries.
              Previously he was a founder, CTO and VP Marketing of Blue Pumpkin Software, the market leader of workforce
              optimization systems, with over 1,000 customers worldwide and $40M in annual sales. In 2002,
              Blue Pumpkin was 5th on the Inc 500 list of fastest growing private companies. The company was sold in 2005
              for $75M and now is part of Verint Systems (VRNT).  Before that Dr. Matan conducted research in the area
              of optical character recognition and computer learning systems at Bell Labs and at Stanford University.
            </p>
